{"tid":2451032,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美商務部傳喚多間中國通訊技術公司查國安威脅　FCC著手撤兩電信商營運許可","createTime":"2021-03-17T22:59:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T07:05:34.000Z","uid":204533,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c4fdb656194c16af205d1ca1112ebe873b8e24dd","tid":2451032,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T22:59:37.000Z","msg":"美國商務部周三（3/17）表示，已發出傳票給多家在美國提供資訊及通訊技術服務的中國公司，以調查他們是否構成國家安全威脅。另外，聯邦傳播委員會（FCC）周三也指出，已著手撤銷中國聯通美洲（China Unicom Americas）、太平洋網路（Pacific Networks）及其全資子公司信通電話（ComNet）在美國提供電信服務的營運許可。<br />\n<br />\n商務部長雷蒙多（Gina Raimondo）透過聲明表示，「北京進行削弱我們的技術優勢，以及威脅我們的聯盟的行為。傳票將可收集資訊，讓我們能夠確立最能保護美國公司、美國勞工及美國國家安全的可能行動。」<br />\n<br />\n聲明中並未點名任何公司，不過，前總統川普政府曾將華為和中興通訊當作目標，封殺他們參與美國電信基礎設施。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，<strong><span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"xx-large\">FCC表示，已展開撤銷中國聯通美洲、太平洋網路（Pacific Networks）及信通電話營運許可的程序。<br />\n<br />\nFCC在去年4月對前述2間中國電信公司以及中國電信（China Telecom Corp Ltd）發出「要求說明理由的命令」，要求他們須表明不受中國政府控制，否則美方可能以國家安全為由，關閉其在美業務。</span></strong></span></strong><br />\n<br />\nFCC周三指出，這些中國公司「在現階段無法排除對其美國營運許可的嚴重擔憂」。FCC已在去年12月展開撤銷中國最大電信公司中國電信營運許可程序，中國電信已獲在美提供電信服務許可近20年。<br />\n<br />\nFCC委員斯塔克斯（Geoffrey Starks）指出，許多中國電信營運商「自身也擁有在美國運作的數據中心」。他續指，<strong><span class=\"red\">FCC目前缺乏「應對此前在國安威脅」的權力。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nFCC上周五（3/12）根據一項保護美國通訊網路法案，將5家中國公司指定為國安威脅，這5間公司分別為華為、中興通訊、海能達、杭州海康威視及大華科技。（盧宥竹／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"4beb2256cdf3a985e30b6ad62dcc52e731fe5131","tid":2451032,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T23:03:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210318/HX6Y5XGIMBAGHLD23PNTLU7Z3E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210318%2FHX6Y5XGIMBAGHLD23PNTLU7Z3E%2F&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2Q%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=ebcad7b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210318%2FHX6Y5XGIMBAGHLD23PNTLU7Z3E%2F&h=1269e1e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210318/HX6Y5XGIMBAGHLD23PNTLU7Z3E/</a>"},{"pid":"9248d236a57922b2bd5d7baa268f376f7322aad3","tid":2451032,"uid":283494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T23:11:23.000Z","msg":"日日有action<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7dada540e11f14db3c9e42b96ca0ee064dd622c","tid":2451032,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T23:13:11.000Z","msg":"以為兩電係中國移動同中國電信 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bfd77cf95bec106cfd45973e2edf6ed82ade89e","tid":2451032,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9248d236a57922b2bd5d7baa268f376f7322aad3","tid":2451032,"uid":283494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T23:11:23.000Z","msg":"日日有action<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T23:13:57.000Z","msg":"希望真係做, 唔好查完話無事<br />\n而且仲有好多野.....EG 抖陰 微信 大學背後資金等...."},{"pid":"1cae73dc80786c4629c5b9f4f44afcf2e6352384","tid":2451032,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T23:14:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5decb931514f66fd77e1f7e84c29cbaecee7b5aa","tid":2451032,"uid":168818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T23:36:14.000Z","msg":"btw 小米係咪已無事？"},{"pid":"adec61b9eb873a47397502dfb12b9e65b51b06f8","tid":2451032,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T23:36:57.000Z","msg":"All action ! No talk !"},{"pid":"8222d94f6ad757731ac5771d050edbd26e707b60","tid":2451032,"uid":104684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T06:48:52.000Z","msg":"No bullshit! Let's Sanction<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.g